    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6256347/" class="title-link">曹操也得顺势而为</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6256347"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/15810199/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u15810199-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/15810199/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">雪落无痕非我也</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-01"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-01 09:40:44</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6256347_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  第九本中重点讲了三件事儿：曹操终于承认了天下无法在其有生之年完成统一、也难以亲自篡汉；曹操终于决定将继嗣的天平倾向于他并不很喜欢的曹丕；曹操终于放弃了“唯才是举”的人事路线。实际上，是曹操终于顺势而为了，这并非是他进入老境力不从心，而是他开始看清楚历史大势...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
